As well as being a chart-topping singer, Tinie Tempah is without a doubt one of Britain's most stylish men.

So, it's hardly surprising that Tinie, who counts fashionista Cheryl Fernandez-Versini as one of his nearest and dearest, has been hand-picked to be The London Collections: Men ambassador.

The 26-year-old replaces Nick Grimshaw in the role, which sees him promoting all things men's fashion ahead of the London Fashion Week this month.

